
native->implementation of sleep method is not implemented by java,it is implemented by native
languages like C,C++

Prevent Thread Execution Methods

1]public static native void sleep(long millis);      //CTE: throws InterruptedException
2]public static native void yield();
3]public final void join();                         //throws InterruptedException

//Deprecated methods
4]public final void suspend();
5]public final void resume();
6]public final void stop();
7]public void destroy();

//Interrupting a Thread methods
8]public void interrupt();
9]public boolean isInterrupted();
10]public static boolean interrupted();